\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
Department-7 may not be the richest organization in the world, nor is it the best networked, but it does provide agents with some of the most unique equipment in the fi
eld. Besides having access to all publicly available mundane and magic items, members of Department-7 each receive the following:
\par }{\b Synchronicity Watch: }{A wrist or pocket watch that allows agents to move through crowds more easily than usual. Once per day, the watch can be used to activate a limited version of the }{\i synchronicity }{
spell. It works exactly the same way as the spell except that the duration is only 10 rounds.
